Breadth-First Search (BFS) implementation.

cpdef functions:

- bfs_csr
    Compute BFS tree using CSR format (forward traversal). Returns predecessors.
- bfs_csc
    Compute BFS tree using CSC format (backward traversal). Returns predecessors.
"""

